se.lth.cs.docforia

Class DocumentEngine

  • java.lang.Object
    • se.lth.cs.docforia.DocumentEngine
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MemoryDocumentEngine, ViewEngine

    public abstract class DocumentEngine
extends Object
    Document database functions Provides a set of functions used by the query engine to retrieve and find data. Remarks: The implementing storage system should override and provide optimized functions. The default implemention only provides simple O(n) searching algorithms for easier implementation.
